data.description:
4654 Lucerne Lakes Blvd E APT 206, Lake Worth, FL 33467 is a apartment home that contains 1,056 sq ft and was built in 1989. It contains 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This home last sold for $135,000 in April 2021. 
 
The Zestimate for this house is $230,900. The Rent Zestimate for this home is $2,294/mo.
